{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1780907641353,"sessionID":"ses_159a25826ffeGycQmqCQ1cpr4r","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"mk-spec-memory_memory_match_triggers","callID":"call_4XDzYSKnCY8FvZ5kTOKCuH5q","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"prompt":"You are a deep-review agent running a fan-out lineage.\n\nRead .opencode/skills/deep-review/SKILL.md and execute the review loop with these parameters:\n  spec_folder: skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep\n  config.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-6\n  session_id: fanout-gpt55-6-1780906361310-a9e1uj\n  executor: cli-opencode model=openai/gpt-5.5-fast\n  loop_type: review\n  config.maxIterations: 1\n\nThe step_resolve_artifact_root step will bind artifact_dir to .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-6 via the\nconfig.fanout_lineage_artifact_dir override — do NOT run the resolveArtifactRoot node\ncommand; bind artifact_dir directly to the override value.\n\nRun phase_init, phase_main_loop (to convergence OR config.maxIterations, whichever comes first), and phase_synthesis.\nWrite all outputs to .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-6. Do not touch any path outside .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep/review/lineages/gpt55-6.\n\nWhen complete, output a single line: FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:gpt55-6","specFolder":"skilled-agent-orchestration/139-multi-model-deep","tenantId":"","userId":"","agentId":"","limit":3,"session_id":"fanout-gpt55-6-1780906361310-a9e1uj","turnNumber":1,"include_cognitive":true},"output":"{\n  \"summary\": \"Error: sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55-6-1780906361310-a9e1uj\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n  \"data\": {\n    \"error\": \"sessionId \\\"fanout-gpt55-6-1780906361310-a9e1uj\\\" does not match a server-managed session. Omit sessionId to start a new server-generated session and reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by the server.\",\n    \"code\": \"E_SESSION_SCOPE\",\n    \"details\": {\n      \"requestedSessionId\": \"fanout-gpt55-6-1780906361310-a9e1uj\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"hints\": [\n    \"Omit session_id to start a new server-generated session, or reuse the effectiveSessionId returned by memory_context.\"\n  ],\n  \"meta\": {\n    \"tool\": \"memory_match_triggers\",\n    \"tokenCount\": 224,\n    \"cacheHit\": false,\n    \"isError\": true,\n    \"severity\": \"error\",\n    \"tokenBudget\": 3500\n  }\n}","metadata":{"truncated":false},"title":"","time":{"start":1780907638598,"end":1780907641350}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0cbff24cdeddef65016a267e6f1a788191a768eb4344241a89"}},"id":"prt_ea65de206001PCKZSgME7Y7Krl","sessionID":"ses_159a25826ffeGycQmqCQ1cpr4r","messageID":"msg_ea65daa520011lJIXFXeQ7Kxf8"}}
